<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#1a237e">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    
    <meta name="description" content="معهد دار الخبراء العالي للتدريب - برامج تدريبية معتمدة | ابدأ مستقبلك المهني الآن">
    <meta name="keywords" content="معهد تدريب, برامج معتمدة, تدريب مهني, شهادات, الرياض, السعودية">
    <title>معهد دار الخبراء - برامج تدريبية معتمدة</title>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <!-- AOS Animations -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Swiper -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@10/swiper-bundle.min.css">

    <style>
        /* ============================================
           Color Variables - Royal Blue, Silver, White
           ============================================ */
        :root {
            --royal: #1a237e;
            --royal-dark: #0d1547;
            --royal-mid: #283593;
            --royal-light: #3949ab;
            --royal-soft: #e8eaf6;
            --silver: #b0bec5;
            --silver-light: #eceff1;
            --silver-mid: #cfd8dc;
            --silver-dark: #78909c;
            --accent: #7986cb;
            --gold: #c9a84c;
            --gold-light: #f5e5b0;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #1a1a2e;
            --text-mid: #455a64;
            --text-light: #90a4ae;
            --bg-light: #f8faff;
            --bg-section: #f0f4ff;
            --shadow-sm: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,35,126,0.08);
            --shadow-md: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,35,126,0.10);
            --shadow-lg: 0 16px 48px rgba(26,35,126,0.18);
            --radius: 16px;
            --radius-sm: 10px;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Dark Mode */
        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --white: #0d1547;
            --text-dark: #e8eaf6;
            --text-mid: #9fa8da;
            --text-light: #5c6bc0;
            --bg-light: #0d1547;
            --bg-section: #111b4a;
            --silver-light: #1a237e;
            --silver-mid: #283593;
            --shadow-md: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            direction: rtl;
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        /* ===== Loading Screen ===== */
        #loader {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: var(--royal-dark);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 9999;
            transition: opacity 0.6s, visibility 0.6s;
        }
        #loader.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
        }
        .loader-logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--silver), var(--silver-light));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .loader-bar {
            width: 200px;
            height: 3px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            border-radius: 3px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .loader-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--silver), var(--accent));
            animation: load 2s ease-in-out forwards;
        }
        .loader-text {
            color: var(--silver);
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.08); }
        }
        @keyframes load {
            from { width: 0; }
            to { width: 100%; }
        }

        /* ===== Header / Navigation ===== */
        #navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 16px 0;
            background: rgba(13,21,71,0.8);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        #navbar.scrolled {
            background: rgba(13,21,71,0.97);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            padding: 10px 0;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .nav-logo-circle {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--silver), var(--silver-light));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--royal);
            text-align: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .nav-brand-text {
            color: #fff;
        }
        .nav-brand-text strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .nav-brand-text small {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }
        .nav-link-item {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8) !important;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 6px 14px !important;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-link-item:hover,
        .nav-link-item.active {
            color: #fff !important;
            background: rgba(121,134,203,0.2);
        }
        .btn-register-nav {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--silver), #d0d8e0);
            color: var(--royal) !important;
            font-weight: 700 !important;
            padding: 8px 20px !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-register-nav:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
        }
        .theme-toggle {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: #fff;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .theme-toggle:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        /* ===== 1. HERO SECTION ===== */
        #hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1547 0%, #1a237e 45%, #283593 70%, #1a237e 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 80px;
        }
        .hero-bg-shapes {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-shape {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
        }
        .hs1 {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: rgba(121,134,203,0.15);
            top: -100px;
            left: -100px;
        }
        .hs2 {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
            bottom: -100px;
            right: -50px;
        }
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(176,190,197,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
            color: var(--silver);
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
        }
        .hero-badge-dot {
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--gold);
            animation: blink 1.5s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
        }
        .hero-title span {
            color: var(--silver);
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.85);
            line-height: 1.9;
            max-width: 520px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.6s both;
        }
        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.8s both;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--silver), #d0d8e0);
            color: var(--royal);
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(176,190,197,0.4);
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.4);
            padding: 13px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
        }
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-color: rgba(176,190,197,0.7);
        }
        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 48px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 1s both;
        }
        .hero-stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero-stat-num {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .hero-stat-num span {
            color: var(--gold);
        }
        .hero-stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.7);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.6);
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 1.5s both;
        }
        .scroll-arrow {
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            font-size: 20px;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(8px); }
        }

        /* ===== General Sections ===== */
        .section-pad {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .section-pad-sm {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .section-bg {
            background: var(--bg-section);
        }
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 56px;
        }
        .section-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--royal-soft);
            color: var(--royal-light);
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .section-line {
            width: 56px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--royal-light), var(--silver));
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: 12px auto;
        }
        .section-desc {
            color: var(--text-mid);
            font-size: 15px;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* ===== 2. ACCREDITATIONS ===== */
        .accreditation-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.2);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .accreditation-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        .accred-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .accreditation-card h4 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .accreditation-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ===== 3. PROGRAMS ===== */
        .program-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.25);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
            height: 100%;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .program-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
        .program-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--royal-mid), var(--royal-light));
            padding: 28px 24px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .program-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30px;
            left: -30px;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }
        .program-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
            color: #f0d080;
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 3px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .program-icon {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .program-header h3 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .program-header p {
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.8);
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .program-body {
            padding: 24px;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .program-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .p-meta-chip {
            background: var(--royal-soft);
            color: var(--royal-light);
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .program-features {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .program-features li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            padding: 7px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .program-features li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .program-features li i {
            color: var(--royal-light);
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .program-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .btn-program {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--royal), var(--royal-light));
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 13px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-program:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(26,35,126,0.3);
        }
        .btn-program-outline {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--royal);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--royal);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 13px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-program-outline:hover {
            background: var(--royal-soft);
        }

        /* ===== 4. WHY US ===== */
        .why-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }
        .why-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.2);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 28px 24px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .why-item:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        .why-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--royal-soft);
            color: var(--royal-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .why-item h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .why-item p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ===== 5. TESTIMONIALS ===== */
        .testimonial-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.25);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 28px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .testimonial-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .testimonial-quote {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--royal-soft);
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .testimonial-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .testimonial-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .t-avatar {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--royal-light), var(--accent));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .t-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--royal);
        }
        .t-program {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }
        .stars {
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        /* ===== 6. TRAINERS ===== */
        .trainer-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.25);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 30px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
            height: 100%;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .trainer-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
        .trainer-avatar {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--royal-light), var(--accent));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #fff;
            border: 3px solid var(--royal-soft);
        }
        .trainer-card h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .trainer-spec {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--royal-soft);
            color: var(--royal-light);
            font-size: 12px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .trainer-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .trainer-exp {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ===== 7. PARTNERS ===== */
        .partners-section {
            background: var(--silver-light);
        }
        .partner-logo {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 16px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--royal);
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 70px;
        }
        .partner-logo:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* ===== 8. GALLERY ===== */
        .gallery-item {
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .gallery-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--royal-soft), var(--silver-light));
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--royal-light);
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .gallery-placeholder i {
            font-size: 32px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        /* ===== 9. REGISTRATION FORM ===== */
        .form-section {
            background: var(--bg-section);
        }
        .form-wrapper-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(26,35,126,0.12);
        }
        .form-sidebar {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--royal-dark), var(--royal-mid));
            padding: 40px 32px;
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .form-sidebar::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -80px;
            left: -80px;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(121,134,203,0.15);
        }
        .form-sidebar h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--silver);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .form-sidebar > p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.8);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .form-steps {
            position: relative;
        }
        .form-step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step-circle {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(176,190,197,0.15);
            border: 2px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.4);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--silver);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .step-info strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .step-info span {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.7);
        }
        .form-body {
            padding: 40px 32px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--royal);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,35,126,0.1);
        }
        .form-group textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 80px;
        }
        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--silver), #d0d8e0);
            color: var(--royal);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(176,190,197,0.4);
        }
        .form-note {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* ===== 10. CONTACT ===== */
        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .contact-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--royal-soft);
            color: var(--royal-light);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .contact-content h4 {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--royal);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .contact-content p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .contact-content a {
            color: var(--royal-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .contact-content a:hover {
            color: var(--royal);
        }

        /* ===== 11. FOOTER ===== */
        .footer {
            background: var(--royal-dark);
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.8);
            padding: 60px 0 20px;
        }
        .footer-col h4 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        .footer-col ul {
            list-style: none;
        }
        .footer-col ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer-col ul li a {
            color: rgba(176,190,197,0.8);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .footer-col ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--silver);
        }
        .footer-socials {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .footer-social-link {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(176,190,197,0.15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--silver);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .footer-social-link:hover {
            background: var(--silver);
            color: var(--royal-dark);
        }
        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.2);
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* ===== Responsive ===== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .form-wrapper-card {
                flex-direction: column !important;
            }
            .form-sidebar {
                padding: 30px 24px;
            }
            .form-body {
                padding: 30px 24px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            #hero {
                padding-top: 70px;
            }
            .hero-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .btn-primary,
            .btn-outline {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .hero-stats {
                gap: 20px;
            }
            .section-pad {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }
            .why-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .program-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .btn-program,
            .btn-program-outline {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .navbar-collapse {
                background: rgba(13,21,71,0.98);
                padding: 10px 0;
                border-top: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.1);
            }
            .section-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .hero-stats {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .hero-stat {
                flex: 1;
                min-width: 150px;
            }
            .container-fluid {
                padding-left: 15px;
                padding-right: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Loading Screen -->
    <div id="loader">
        <div class="loader-logo">دخ</div>
        <div class="loader-bar">
            <div class="loader-fill"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="loader-text">جاري التحميل...</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Header (Navigation) -->
    <nav id="navbar" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="nav-brand" href="#home">
                <div class="nav-logo-circle">دخ</div>
                <div class="nav-brand-text">
                    <strong>دار الخبراء</strong>
                    <small>معهد التدريب</small>
                </div>
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-link-item" href="#hero">الرئيسية</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-link-item" href="#programs">البرامج</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-link-item" href="#why">لماذا نحن</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-link-item" href="#testimonials">آرائكم</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-link-item" href="#contact">التواصل</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" title="تغيير المظهر">
                            <i class="fas fa-moon"></i>
                        </button>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#register" class="btn btn-register-nav ms-2">سجل الآن</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 1. HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg-shapes">
            <div class="hero-shape hs1"></div>
            <div class="hero-shape hs2"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container-fluid position-relative z-1">
            <div class="row align-items-center min-vh-100">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                    <div class="hero-badge">
                        <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
                        <span>معتمد من المؤسسة العامة للتدريب التقني والمهني</span>
                    </div>

                    <h1 class="hero-title">ابدأ <span>مستقبلك المهني</span> مع برامج تدريبية معتمدة</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        برامج تدريبية متخصصة تجمع بين النظرية والتطبيق العملي مع كادر تدريبي متميز وشهادات معترف بها دولياً
                    </p>

                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <button class="btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#registerModal">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle ms-2"></i>سجل الآن
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn-outline" onclick="document.getElementById('programs').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left ms-2"></i>استعرض البرامج
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-stats">
                        <div class="hero-stat">
                            <div class="hero-stat-num"><span>25</span>+</div>
                            <div class="hero-stat-label">برنامج تدريبي</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hero-stat">
                            <div class="hero-stat-num"><span>5000</span>+</div>
                            <div class="hero-stat-label">متدرب</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hero-stat">
                            <div class="hero-stat-num"><span>15</span>+</div>
                            <div class="hero-stat-label">سنة خبرة</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 text-center">
                    <div style="
                        width: 100%;
                        height: 400px;
                        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(176,190,197,0.2), rgba(121,134,203,0.15));
                        border-radius: 20px;
                        display: flex;
                        align-items: center;
                        justify-content: center;
                        border: 1px solid rgba(176,190,197,0.3);
                    ">
                        <div style="text-align: center;">
                            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap" style="font-size: 80px; color: var(--silver); opacity: 0.5; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;"></i>
                            <p style="color: rgba(176,190,197,0.6); font-size: 16px;">صورة توضيحية للبرامج التدريبية</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="scroll-indicator">
                <span>اسحب لأسفل</span>
                <span class="scroll-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. ACCREDITATIONS SECTION -->
    <section class="section-pad">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="section-tag">الاعتمادات والشهادات</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">معتمدون رسمياً</h2>
                <div class="section-line"></div>
                <p class="section-desc">برامجنا معتمدة من الجهات الحكومية والدولية المعترف بها</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="accreditation-card">
                        <div class="accred-icon"><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i></div>
                        <h4>المؤسسة العامة للتدريب</h4>
                        <p>معتمد من المؤسسة العامة للتدريب التقني والمهني - السعودية</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="accreditation-card">
                        <div class="accred-icon"><i class="fas fa-award"></i></div>
                        <h4>ISO 9001:2015</h4>
                        <p>شهادة الجودة الدولية في إدارة الجودة</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="accreditation-card">
                        <div class="accred-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
                        <h4>الشهادات الدولية</h4>
                        <p>شهادات معترف بها عالمياً في مختلف المجالات</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="accreditation-card">
                        <div class="accred-icon"><i class="fas fa-check-double"></i></div>
                        <h4>ترخيص رقم 12345</h4>
                        <p>رقم الترخيص الرسمي من وزارة التعليم والتدريب</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. PROGRAMS SECTION -->
    <section id="programs" class="section-pad section-bg">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="section-tag">البرامج التدريبية</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">برامجنا المتخصصة</h2>
                <div class="section-line"></div>
                <p class="section-desc">اختر من مجموعة برامج تدريبية متخصصة وفقاً لاحتياجاتك المهنية</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row g-4">
                <!-- Program 1 -->
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="program-card">
                        <div class="program-header">
                            <span class="program-badge">معتمد</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-network-wired program-icon"></i>
                            <h3>دبلوم الشبكات</h3>
                            <p>برنامج متخصص في هندسة الشبكات</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="program-body">
                            <div class="program-meta">
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-clock ms-1"></i>6 أشهر</span>
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-half ms-1"></i>240 ساعة</span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="program-features">
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>شهادة معتمدة</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>تدريب عملي</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>متابعة توظيفية</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="program-buttons">
                                <button class="btn-program">التفاصيل</button>
                                <button class="btn-program-outline" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#registerModal">تسجيل</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Program 2 -->
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="program-card">
                        <div class="program-header">
                            <span class="program-badge">معتمد</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-users program-icon"></i>
                            <h3>إدارة الموارد البشرية</h3>
                            <p>برنامج متخصص في إدارة الموارد البشرية</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="program-body">
                            <div class="program-meta">
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-clock ms-1"></i>4 أشهر</span>
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-half ms-1"></i>160 ساعة</span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="program-features">
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>شهادة معتمدة</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>حالات عملية</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>دعم مستمر</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="program-buttons">
                                <button class="btn-program">التفاصيل</button>
                                <button class="btn-program-outline" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#registerModal">تسجيل</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Program 3 -->
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="program-card">
                        <div class="program-header">
                            <span class="program-badge">معتمد</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line program-icon"></i>
                            <h3>التسويق الرقمي</h3>
                            <p>برنامج متخصص في التسويق الرقمي والإعلانات</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="program-body">
                            <div class="program-meta">
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-clock ms-1"></i>3 أشهر</span>
                                <span class="p-meta-chip"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-half ms-1"></i>120 ساعة</span>
                            </div>
                            <ul class="program-features">
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>شهادة معتمدة</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>مشاريع حقيقية</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>شهادة احترافية</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="program-buttons">
                                <button class="btn-program">التفاصيل</button>
                                <button class="btn-program-outline" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#registerModal">تسجيل</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-5" data-aos="fade-up">
                <button class="btn-primary">
                    عرض جميع البرامج <i class="fas fa-arrow-left ms-2"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. WHY US SECTION -->
    <section id="why" class="section-pad">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="section-tag">مميزاتنا</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">لماذا تختار دار الخبراء؟</h2>
                <div class="section-line"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="why-grid">
                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-user"></i></div>
                    <h3>كادر تدريبي متميز</h3>
                    <p>مدربون متخصصون بخبرة عملية واسعة وشهادات معترف بها دولياً</p>
                </div>

                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i></div>
                    <h3>شهادات معتمدة</h3>
                    <p>برامجنا معتمدة من الجهات الحكومية والدولية المعترف بها</p>
                </div>

                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-laptop"></i></div>
                    <h3>تطبيق عملي فوري</h3>
                    <p>كل درس يحتوي على تطبيقات عملية مباشرة وحالات واقعية</p>
                </div>

                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
                    <h3>توظيف وتطوير وظيفي</h3>
                    <p>متابعة توظيفية مستمرة وفرص عمل مع الشركاء الموثوقين</p>
                </div>

                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i></div>
                    <h3>دعم فني متواصل</h3>
                    <p>فريق دعم متواصل طوال فترة البرنامج والمتابعة بعد التخرج</p>
                </div>

                <div class="why-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
                    <h3>مرونة في الجدول</h3>
                    <p>اختر الأوقات المناسبة لك - دوام صباحي أو مسائي</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. TESTIMONIALS SECTION -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="section-pad section-bg">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="section-tag">آراء المتدربين</div>
